==Legacy==
A sequel, ''[[Mugsy's Revenge]]'' was published two years later, and ported to the [[Commodore 64]] and [[Amstrad CPC]].  Russel Comte, a leading member of the design team, went on to work as an artist on a number of other significant computer game titles.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mobygames.com/developer/sheet/view/developerId,808/|title=Russel Comte Video Game Credits and Biography - MobyGames|work=MobyGames|accessdate=27 June 2015}}</ref>

